45:47.511 --> 45:50.139
Hi. I'm Burke.

45:51.248 --> 45:52.840
Burke Ryan!

45:53.917 --> 45:56.215
Ellie, you didn't tell me
you were dating a celebrity.

45:56.286 --> 45:58.277
